pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: content-left-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 0, 6, 720]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: content-top-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 0, 1280, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: content-section-name
    elementType: text
    bounds: [900, 16, 340, 22]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: 02 文献综述与理论基础

  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [40, 24, 840, 36]
    content:
      fontSize: 26
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>相关工作综述与研究空白分析</strong></p>

  - elementId: title-separator
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 68, 1200, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$borderGray"

  # Bullet 1
  - elementId: bullet-1-num
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 88, 30, 30]
    shapeName: ellipse
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: bullet-1-num-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [40, 88, 30, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "1"

  - elementId: bullet-1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [86, 88, 1154, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>传统方法回顾</strong></p>

  - elementId: bullet-1-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [86, 122, 1154, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p>早期研究以规则驱动和统计建模为主，在封闭场景中取得了一定成效，但泛化能力受限，难以应对真实分布偏移。</p>

  - elementId: sep-1
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 162, 1200, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$borderGray"

  # Bullet 2
  - elementId: bullet-2-num
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 178, 30, 30]
    shapeName: ellipse
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$secondary"

  - elementId: bullet-2-num-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [40, 178, 30, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "2"

  - elementId: bullet-2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [86, 178, 1154, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>深度学习方法进展</strong></p>

  - elementId: bullet-2-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [86, 212, 1154, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p>基于 CNN/Transformer 的方法在多个基准上达到 SOTA，尤其在大规模预训练范式下效果显著提升，成为当前主流。</p>

  - elementId: sep-2
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 252, 1200, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$borderGray"

  # Bullet 3
  - elementId: bullet-3-num
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 268, 30, 30]
    shapeName: ellipse
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: bullet-3-num-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [40, 268, 30, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "3"

  - elementId: bullet-3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [86, 268, 1154, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>现有方法的局限性</strong></p>

  - elementId: bullet-3-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [86, 302, 1154, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p>现有方法普遍存在数据依赖重、计算成本高、跨域迁移弱等问题，在低资源场景下表现大幅下降。</p>

  - elementId: sep-3
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 342, 1200, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$borderGray"

  # Bullet 4
  - elementId: bullet-4-num
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 358, 30, 30]
    shapeName: ellipse
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: bullet-4-num-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [40, 358, 30, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "4"

  - elementId: bullet-4-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [86, 358, 1154, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>本研究切入点</strong></p>

  - elementId: bullet-4-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [86, 392, 1154, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p>针对以上空白，本研究提出在 [关键方向] 上的改进方案，通过 [核心机制] 解决效率与泛化之间的矛盾。</p>

  # 结论强调框
  - elementId: conclusion-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 448, 1200, 54]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#E3F0FA"

  - elementId: conclusion-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 448, 1160, 54]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p><strong>研究定位：</strong>本文在充分调研现有工作的基础上，识别关键研究空白，提出具有针对性的技术方案。</p>

  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1200, 680, 50, 24]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "5"
